reviewText: Very well done movie on the man Stephen Foster who created some of the most memorable American music of all time. Unfortunately this movie could never be made in our politically correct culture, but that makes this movie even more important.
A good movie on the life of stephen Foster.
I like the story and I thought the production was good for this time period, but it was not true to fact.
One of my favorite movies, because of the music. I miss good old talent!
